OL,3,CDrop in UK inflation is the lull
OL,4,Cbefore the storm
OL,6,FThe headline annual rate of inflation
OL,7,Ftook a big step down last month to
OL,8,F2.8%.
OL,10,FThe Ofgem price cap was lowered in
OL,11,FApril, dragging household energy bills
OL,12,Fdown with it.
OL,14,FThe disinflationary force was
OL,15,Fstrengthened by the Chancellor's
OL,16,Fdecision to freeze bus and train fares
OL,17,Fand to remove green levies from energy
OL,18,Fbills.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
