OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779286285
OL,3,CDrop in UK inflation is the lull
OL,4,Cbefore the storm
OL,6,FLast April's large increases in water
OL,7,Fbills, vehicle excise duty and
OL,8,FNational Insurance were not repeated
OL,9,Fand airlines and tour operators kept
OL,10,Fprices down as bookings sagged in
OL,11,Fresponse to the war in the Gulf.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,F"The lull before the storm," warns
OL,19,FCapital Economics.
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@\O]
