OL,3,CDrop in UK inflation is the lull
OL,4,Cbefore the storm
OL,6,FThe impact of the ongoing closure of
OL,7,Fthe Strait of Hormuz is already being
OL,8,Ffelt, by motorists and by anyone who
OL,9,Fuses oil to heat their homes.
OL,11,FThe average price of unleaded petrol
OL,12,Freached 152.5 pence a litre at the
OL,13,Fpump yesterday, the highest level
OL,14,Fsince the war began.
OL,16,FAnd the impact of higher fuel prices
OL,17,Fis rippling out, putting upward
OL,18,Fpressure on the cost of almost
OL,19,Feverything.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
