OL,3,CDrop in UK inflation is the lull
OL,4,Cbefore the storm
OL,6,FAnnual food and drink inflation eased
OL,7,Fback to 3% in April, but food and
OL,8,Fdrink producers stand by their
OL,9,Fforecast that it could be running at
OL,10,Fclose to 10% by Christmas, even in a
OL,11,F"best-case scenario".
OL,13,FMost economists expect inflation to
OL,14,Fpick up, albeit not on anything like
OL,15,Fthe scale experienced after Russia
OL,16,Finvaded Ukraine in 2022.
OL,18,FThe government can see the wave coming
OL,19,Fand is trying to get out ahead of it.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@TO]
