OL,3,CDrop in UK inflation is the lull
OL,4,Cbefore the storm
OL,6,FSupermarkets are being asked to
OL,7,Fconsider freezing the prices of
OL,8,Feveryday essentials such as bread,
OL,9,Fbutter, milk and eggs.
OL,11,FSanctions on Russian oil are being
OL,12,Floosened for an "indefinite duration",
OL,13,Fwhile still allowing imports of
OL,14,Frefined products such as jet fuel and
OL,15,Fdiesel from Turkey and India.
OL,17,FMore help is on the way.
OL,26,@tD@QOUtD@eO]
