OL,3,CDrop in UK inflation is the lull
OL,4,Cbefore the storm
OL,6,F"We have already taken #117 off energy
OL,7,Fbills, frozen rail fares, and lifted
OL,8,Fthe two-child limit, and over today
OL,9,Fand tomorrow I will set out the next
OL,10,Fphase of how we will support UK
OL,11,Fhouseholds," the Chancellor said in a
OL,12,Fstatement this morning.
OL,14,F"We have the right economic plan, and
OL,15,Fto change course now would risk our
OL,16,Feconomic stability and leave working
OL,17,Fpeople worse off."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@LO]vD@AOUyD@RO]
